@startuml seq-01-register
' 序列图1：用户注册
title 用户注册序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "register.js" as Front
participant "UserController" as Ctrl
participant "UserService" as Svc
participant "UserMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 填写手机号/邮箱/昵称/密码
Front -> Front: 5栏实时校验(正则)
User -> Front: 点击注册
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/user/register(phone,email,password,nickname)
Ctrl -> Svc: register(phone,email,password,nickname)
Svc -> Svc: MD5加密密码
Svc -> Mapper: insertUser(User)
Mapper -> DB: INSERT INTO user
DB --> Mapper: 影响行数1
Mapper --> Svc: user_id
Svc --> Ctrl: User对象
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:User}
Front -> Front: wx.setStorageSync(userId)
Front -> Front: wx.setStorageSync(token)
Front --> User: 跳转我的页

@enduml
